<figure class="attention-mechanism">
  <div class="attention-mechanism__frame" role="group" aria-labelledby="attention-mechanism-title">
    <header>
      <span>ONE ATTENTION HEAD</span>
      <strong id="attention-mechanism-title">从输入表示到加权输出</strong>
    </header>

    <ol class="attention-mechanism__steps">
      <li>
        <span class="attention-mechanism__number">01</span>
        <strong>输入表示</strong>
        <code>X ∈ ℝⁿˣᵈ</code>
        <small>每行对应一个Token位置</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="attention-mechanism__number">02</span>
        <strong>三组投影</strong>
        <code>Q=XW_Q · K=XW_K · V=XW_V</code>
        <small>Q/K负责匹配，V承载被组合的信息</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="attention-mechanism__number">03</span>
        <strong>两两打分</strong>
        <code>S=QKᵀ/√dₖ</code>
        <small>S是n×n矩阵</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="attention-mechanism__number">04</span>
        <strong>Mask与归一化</strong>
        <code>A=softmax(S+M)</code>
        <small>每一行权重之和为1</small>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="attention-mechanism__number">05</span>
        <strong>组合Value</strong>
        <code>O=AV</code>
        <small>得到每个位置的新表示</small>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <figcaption>这是一层中的一个Attention Head。多头结果还要拼接并投影，随后经过残差连接、归一化和前馈网络。</figcaption>
</figure>

